content.text: You can test your TypeScript skills with W3Schools' Quiz.
content.html: You can test your TypeScript skills with W3Schools' Quiz.

content.text: The test contains 25 questions and there is no time limit.
content.html: The test contains 25 questions and there is no time limit.

content.text: The test is not official, it's just a nice way to see how much you know, or don't know, about TypeScript.
content.html: The test is not official, it's just a nice way to see how much you know, or don't know, about TypeScript.

content.text: You will get 1 point for each correct answer. At the end of the Quiz, your total score will be displayed. Maximum score is 25 points.
content.html: You will get 1 point for each correct answer. At the end of the Quiz, your total score will be displayed. Maximum score is 25 points.

content.text: If you don't know TypeScript, we suggest that you read our TypeScript Tutorial from scratch.
content.html: If you don't know TypeScript, we suggest that you read our TypeScript Tutorial from scratch.
